OL,8,     Gplayed at his mum's funeral to
OL,9,     Gthe Zach Bryan track that helped
OL,10,     Gan ex-soldier with his PTSD.
OL,11,G1630FLocation, Location, Location
OL,12,     GWe revisit Shane, who dreamt of a
OL,13,     Gnew life on the north Kent coast,
OL,14,     Gand Indu and Jason, who wanted a
OL,15,     Gfamily home with potential in
OL,16,     GGuildford. Did they get what they
OL,17,     Gwished for?
